xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.19587-formula59"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2620360x62_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>故方程可以化简为</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19587-formula60"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2620360x63_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>同理</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19587-formula61"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2620360x64_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.19587-formula62"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2620360x65_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.19587-formula63"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2620360x66_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>因为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2620360x67_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>且<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2620360x68_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，所以有如下结论成立：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19587-formula64"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2620360x69_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.19587-formula65"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2620360x70_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>对于上面两个方程，令</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2620360x71_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2620360x72_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula></p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19587-formula66"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2620360x73_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.19587-formula67"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-262